    content: 'Modern CSS has evolved significantly with new features that make building responsive layouts easier than ever. CSS Grid and Flexbox have revolutionized how we create complex layouts, while CSS Variables bring the power of variables to stylesheets.\n\nIn this comprehensive guide, we will explore these modern CSS techniques and learn how to use them effectively in your projects. We will cover practical examples and best practices for creating maintainable and scalable CSS.',
